flowchart TD
    subgraph UserSpace ["User Environment"]
        User["Small Business Owner"]
    end

    subgraph PortalSpace ["Government Business Portal"]
        UI["Web Chat Interface"]
        Agent["Human Support Agent"]
    end

    subgraph AISpace ["Navigator AI Engine"]
        AI["Canberra Business Navigator AI"]
        SessionStore[("Temporary Session Store")]
    end

    subgraph DataSpace ["Government Knowledge Base"]
        GovDocs[("Policy, Grants & Registration Rules")]
    end

    %% Happy Path Flow
    User -->|1. Inputs business type, location & query| UI
    UI -->|2. Forwards query & context| AI
    AI -->|3. Stores sensitive identifiers securely| SessionStore
    AI -->|4. Queries relevant rules & funding criteria| GovDocs
    GovDocs -->|5. Returns verified policy & grant data| AI
    AI -->|6. Generates prioritized checklist & direct links| UI
    UI -->|7. Displays tailored guidance & forms| User

    %% Escalation Path
    UI -->|8. Escalates complex query with chat history| Agent
    Agent -->|9. Provides direct assistance| User